title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-27-2014 THURS
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-27-2014 THURS...PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 2/27/14Thursday, February 27, 2014


New gun laws in Connecticut are making criminals 
         out of lawful gun owners and Glenn is infuriated.

  Also, as more attention is being focused on the Justina Pelletier situation,
     more stories of children being wrongfully taken away from their parents are surfacing.

  Plus, Lee Bright, joins the program to discuss his run against Lindsey Graham
            for the Senate seat in South Carolina.
